      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are operational and have been regularly serviced, the car shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few minor dings, and the interior upholstery is worn with some staining. It is a solid, honest car that performs well but lacks the polish of a newer model.",
