    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, confirms its status as a premier example of the marque. Rigorously inspected and prepared for immediate delivery, this vehicle offers an unrivaled driving experience for those who demand perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
