    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken obsessive care of it\u2014spotless inside and out, smooth as silk on the road, and not a single scratch to be found. If you're looking for that 'new car' magic without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
