    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 high-compression inline-six. This example is mechanically superlative, having undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance overhaul including WPC-treated rod bearings, a Beisan Systems dual-VANOS refresh, and structural subframe reinforcement. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. With a flawless DME report and zero parasitic draw, this is a turn-key masterpiece for the technical purist.",
